sc_cat_item.description: The Mahindra Thar is a rugged, off-road SUV built for adventure and performance. With a 2.0L mStallion petrol engine or a 2.2L mHawk diesel engine, it offers the perfect balance between power and fuel efficiency. The Thar comes with modern features like a touchscreen infotainment system, automatic climate control, and advanced safety features such as ABS and dual airbags. Its 4x4 drivetrain, high ground clearance, and water-wading capability make it a perfect choice for both city driving and off-road expeditions. Available in multiple trims, the Thar is designed to be the ultimate combination of style, comfort, and functionality.
